{"tid":391811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[甚麼才是道德底線？］壞人個仔死左應該祝賀還是扮傷心打句r.i.p.?","createTime":"2017-09-08T05:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T12:17:31.000Z","uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bad7b0d6136cc29edefaf2c9fd3c451c5f00c9","tid":391811,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5e20c5192a560c11c2dec7b43302d9c95d7fb7","tid":391811,"uid":105258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d3655b31d4e6a9a0bb8fc46523a58ee3eb1d7a","tid":391811,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:27:51.000Z","msg":"Rip係比佢個仔的"},{"pid":"6a2bcb4b72e81652273cde488a19f2105916abde","tid":391811,"uid":92353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"敵人死 開心慶祝係理所當然<br />\n唔通拉登同佢屋企人死左美國人要同情可憐佢"},{"pid":"9d16fe2ec559da0d0f898f91fb8c361ad0331d32","tid":391811,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"一條問題 兩個獨立個體"},{"pid":"c5a6ac55c015fd9f4f4a5d82fec08f4f2102a67a","tid":391811,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:35:55.000Z","msg":"慶祝係人之常情<br />\n係街貼揮春，係fb點笑都冇後果<br />\n但係人地地頭慶祝就預左比人收你皮"},{"pid":"38f0417bcc9cc558fa2af9e1716c665be05545e5","tid":391811,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"【蔡若蓮喪子】未查完先定論？教大主席馬時亨：是否想子女被這些人教育？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170908/large/1504858006_38cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170908%2Flarge%2F1504858006_38cc.jpg&h=bd3755f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育大學民主牆昨日出現針對教育局副局長蔡若蓮喪子的涼薄言論，教大校董會主席馬時亨今日回應稱，管理層正調查有關人士是否教大學生，支持管理層積極追查事件始末，強調一定會追究到底。校長張仁良今早表示，仍未確定張貼標語的兩名人士是否教大學生，正在調查中，但馬時亨下午回應時就語帶相關，稱香港人應該反思，是否想張貼有關標語的人士將來做自己子女的老師。他拒絕回應若證實兩人是教大學生，校方是否一定會開除他們，只稱有相關機制及校規跟進事件，校長會比他更清楚。他又認為言論自由有界限，外界應思考今次事件有無超越界線。<br />\n<br />\n另外，下午有傳媒在網上發放聲稱是兩名張貼標語年青人的照片，教大發表聲明，稱校方所有閉路電視的片段，乃用作保安用途，僅供授權人士作內部用途。校方高度關注事件，並對今次有關擷圖外洩，深表遺憾，將通知私隱專員公署跟進。教大呼籲各方停止轉發有關圖片，保障當事人私隱，亦促請各方給予空間，讓校方處理事件<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170908/57184383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170908%2F57184383&d=ZYEtvT0CK1NFNUICGTuMdcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d2c0cf58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170908%2F57184383&h=dd3a79f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170908/57184383</a>"},{"pid":"f64d528db9a3cbce495f929e6ce1a9d301e7d5ef","tid":391811,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/1_22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F07%2F1_22.jpg&h=f44156df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca0404cf538e7542ea5433a89b41f6f61735f0b8","tid":391811,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慶祝係人之常情<br />\n係街貼揮春，係fb點笑都冇後果<br />\n但係人地地頭慶祝就預左比人收你皮</blockquote><br />\n民主牆幾時變左人地地頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04440c0993139c2e27d58fdd03aac0bb485b3d7","tid":391811,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:12:47.000Z","msg":"Rip 係比個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5c06fd3d2df8fe3ab3825530807cd13e0f9be3","tid":391811,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>慶祝係人之常情<br />\n係街貼揮春，係fb點笑都冇後果<br />\n但係人地地頭慶祝就預左比人收你皮</blockquote><br />\n民主牆幾時變左人地地頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學生唔知乜野叫民主牆"},{"pid":"6ba839dfd070eb30f287b3b733fcdae1c1dcb7fd","tid":391811,"uid":531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"連登有條友次次有人死就貼咩唔駛住劏房係福氣，點解冇人話佢涼薄"}]}